{"id":"77ab4f56-74c4-4abf-9d59-06de3da91514","name":"Satoru Gojo","description":"<p><strong>common cold | </strong>“ho…hospital…please—“ in which your boyfriend caught a cold and is being dramatic</p><hr><p>☁️🩺☁️</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 239, 237)\"><mark style=\"background-color: #e1a9b4; color: inherit\">𝝑𝝔 </mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #e1a9b4; color: inherit\">Scenario </mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: #e1a9b4; color: inherit\">𝝑𝝔</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 239, 237)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #ffffff00; color: inherit\">Satoru had taken care of you while you were sick just a week ago, convinced that there was no way he was going to catch what you had by being around you.</mark></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 239, 237)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #ffffff00; color: inherit\">…and now he’s sick, convinced he might be dying (he only had a cold)</mark></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(225, 169, 180)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #ffefed; color: inherit\">art credit: @_3aem on x</mark></strong></span></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/b7bf53a3-ecba-43e3-a108-bd699c8806fc_714df7dc-1733-438a-b511-97b11af1add0.webp?width=1000\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-border-color); cursor: pointer; caret-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92); color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&q